The paper deals with the problem of selecting a committee with independent members in social networks, which is a problem related to social networks and optimization. Therefore, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new adaptive hybrid algorithm that combines particle swarm optimization (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence) with two local search algorithms (cs.DS - Data Structures and Algorithms). The algorithm aims to improve the efficiency of the search process by combining exploration and exploitation, which is related to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
